57typedef enum DataType : uint32_t {
58 DataTypeFloatBit = 0x10000000,
59 DataTypeAlternateEncodingBit = 0x80000000,
60 DataTypeFloat16 = DataTypeFloatBit | 16,
61 DataTypeFloat32 = DataTypeFloatBit | 32,
62 DataTypeBFloat16 = DataTypeAlternateEncodingBit | DataTypeFloat16
63} DataType;
